title: 1 Room Efficiency Apartment in Uptown
posting_body: ['1 room efficiency apartment (247 square feet), on 2nd floor facing South of 3 story quiet house centrally located just off Hennepin Ave in the Uptown/Lake of the Isles area.', 'NEWLY RENOVATED!', 'Brand new floors, new woodwork, new appliances, new light fixtures, new paint, new ceiling, new cabinets, new sink, new shelving, new counter tops and has bonus desk area!', "Located right by Kowalski's grocery store and by several bus lines!", 'Perfect for college grad or just starting out a new job from college.', 'To share bathroom (full bath) with one other tenant.', 'Room includes: cable ready and USI Fiber Internet available!', 'hardwood floor, storage closet, and cute kitchenette.', 'It is an 11\' x 11\' room with a 3\' x 4 1/2\' closet and 3\'3" x 4\'3" desk area.', 'On-site (coin operated) laundry facilities in the basement, also a private fenced-in backyard.', 'Tenant to pay own utilities (averages $105 per month).', 'There is on street parking on the East and South sides of the house.', 'NO PETS whatsoever!!', 'NO SMOKING PROPERTY!!', '(Inside or outside)', 'Available 8/15/22 at the soonest, check with us for a Sept. or Oct. date.', "1 year lease (deposit will be 1 month's rent, $625.00).", 'Good credit and rental history required!', 'Application fee is $45.00.', 'Only one person allowed in this unit.', '** PLEASE NOTE: this unit is 247 sq ft!!', "The dimensions are 11' x 11' for the room, with a 3' x 4 1/2' closet!!", '**']
